Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非主人  對凸守…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守是主人的隨從  不可以抱有這種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過俗話說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是禁忌之物越讓人心潮澎湃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和勇太擁抱過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你是冒牌的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼森大人之後  連主人也有假冒的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人你  對黑炎掌控者…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,產生了愛意？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守接下來有個地方要去  先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要攔我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為隨從  我要把奪走主人之心的竊賊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用黑暗的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人說過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是得益於黑炎掌控者  才能將邪王真眼守護至今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份強烈的思念  一定也已經傳達到了黑炎掌控者那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已侍奉主人兩年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨從對主人可是瞭若指掌的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心  沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  你和小鳥遊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該由我來告白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡小鳥遊同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並不是因為她身材好或者可愛什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  那傢伙的中二病真是沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是普通的中二病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她其實也有自己的煩惱  還是挺可憐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  也不是同情什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了  別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上別人不需要理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到你說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真噁心  真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛啊  難得我好心聽你傾訴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒想跟你傾訴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為你說「要是不說我就在班裡散播些有的沒的」來威脅我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  你也夠幸運的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學也是可愛女生選拔第四名的強力選手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼好的女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼好的女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到有一天  你會和這麼好的女孩發生那樣的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜  我對肉體接觸還沒有經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  白癡嗎你是白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.07,0:06:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  於是我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個妹子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枯茗學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  請和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起參加後夜祭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:07:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要看你的三腳貓演技
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是演戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說為什麼你會在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們要練習明天的表演了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富樫君和小鳥遊同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再提他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守現在心情很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可沒空陪你瞎鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來那兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都已經回去了  兩人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑炎掌控者他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說有重要的話要告訴主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就一起走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵從盟約  聽我命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵從盟約  聽我命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵從盟約  聽我命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔導石  可以用來實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凸守給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望的內容不能告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  我也沒問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在強烈的願望下  魔導石會散發熱量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨…  了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶傘…  了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:08:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我也有話要對勇太說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關係到最高機密的重要之事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也有話要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在這裡也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能一直這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗澤克斯原始型 MkⅡ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這全名念得還真順啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好沒掉到下面的河裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:09:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈光在穿梭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:20.60,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何も言わない背中向けをして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.16,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}なんて言えばいいのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:26.35,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好きになるのに　理由はないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:29.54,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}勇気の無さに　言い訳ばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:32.60,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}流星群を眺めていたら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:35.70,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}きらきらって音がするみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:38.74,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そんないきなりな様子が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.66,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君との出會いを立ち會える
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:46.93,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}戀のカケラは今　一つに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:53.16,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}安っぽいことだけ葉えても
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:59.26,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君に屆かないかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:04.95,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}でも何も言わないままな時に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:09.90,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}消えちゃうかも知れない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:12.02,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あの星みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:17.16,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今ここで抱いてるのを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:23.43,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}どうしたら笑ってくれますか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:29.60,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}天とつないで星座にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:36.52,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その指で
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:51.02,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}背中合わせじゃなくて　こっちを向いて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:12:00.25,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そして隣を歩きたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:20.60,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}默默地轉過身去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.16,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不知該怎麼表達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:26.35,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}明明如此地喜歡著  無需理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:29.54,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻又只因沒有勇氣  藉口不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:32.60,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}抬頭眺望流星之雨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:35.70,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}閃耀著劃過星空的美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:38.74,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那樣稍縱即逝的幾秒間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.66,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}見證著你我的眷眷之心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:46.93,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛戀的碎片  此刻合為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:53.16,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}小小心願即便實現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:59.26,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}也許無法傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:04.95,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但在你猶豫的沉默中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:09.90,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}或許會隨之慢慢消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:12.02,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如同那顆星星一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:17.16,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}見證我們愛戀的擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:23.43,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要怎樣才能得到你的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:29.60,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我的手指  連接天際
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:36.52,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}連接那片見證我們的星雲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:51.02,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要背對背  請看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:12:00.25,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}然後願並肩走向永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該我先說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼已經決定了由我先來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是黑炎掌控者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不算不算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易才想好的呢  我要說了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被黑暗火焰所擁抱之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與黑炎掌控者締結戀人之…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不玩了啦  總之…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被黑暗火焰所擁抱之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與黑炎掌控者  締結戀人之契約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候一般不是應該到懷裡來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害羞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把手給我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拇指的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用小拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  今天好晚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  樟葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原告對被告還抱有任何感情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只想儘快與被告脫離關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水準又下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情不能在家裡說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓六花聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從義大利的總店寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀請我去進修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有理由拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還真的很了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都在懷疑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這不是挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花她一定也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白我的意思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能讓她一個人住在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要讓媽媽代替我來和她一起生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花的媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼看…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得她們能好好相處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花其實並不討厭她媽媽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該就沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經好幾次試圖和六花交流
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於隱瞞爸爸狀況的事  也向她道過歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了  十花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了  請幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的話她一定會聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你對她說  讓她正經一些…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花現在已經足夠正經了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那個眼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於她來說就是自我保護的盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花一定什麼都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是心裡總有些無法消除的隔閡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她才會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過這些行為  來保護她要保護的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她肯定不想再失去那些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她聽從您和媽媽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣接受現實的話  那一切就都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是不希望這樣的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束又有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,境界線和邪王真眼都是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼找都是見不到爸爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定她的那些話  又能解決什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她所尋找的東西是永遠都得不到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一味地肯定她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不負責任的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:31.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝士馬鈴薯一份  謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有人氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看她們現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實背後的勾心鬥角可厲害著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不想幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟外面嘎巴脆裡面黏乎乎的芝士馬鈴薯一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  小鳥遊同學和富樫君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是去換衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的表演一定能把客人全都搶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是森大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我森大…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤  還有鈴木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  初中畢業以來頭一次見面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年多大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,716歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在捉蜥蜴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢說我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤你不也曾經把嘴唇塗成紫色來裝病弱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…  佐藤你還幹過這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴木你不也說過你發現了什麼妖精嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還妖精呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中二病的互掐還真是危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道會被曝出怎樣的黑歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的較量  還沒分出勝負呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天特地將戰錘的威力增至平時的四倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.85,0:16:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是個笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定她的那些話  又能解決什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一味地肯定她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不負責任的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太  好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要兩眼放光啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的絕招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「在黑暗火焰的懷抱中消失吧！」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太  來說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你過一會兒還是要演的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗火焰的懷抱中消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點威力都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西能有什麼威力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  要屈膝跨腿猛地出手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓外套下擺隨風舞動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗火焰的懷抱中消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是組合動作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  雖然我是沒什麼幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小手指
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有沒有一個叫小鳥遊六花的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請把這個交給她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  我這就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在應該還不想見到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是不負責任嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡發什麼呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演的時間快到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在剛好來了很多觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼罩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  一年一度的小絕活大賽現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎各位隨時踴躍登台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.46,0:19:50.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我們趕緊進入正題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有請第一位同學上臺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一號  二年三班  原田慎也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:55.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大家帶來模仿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:56.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模仿教導主任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我和那個中二貨想辦法扛過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙竟然還真的打過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然會說出那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份便當
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一些溫熱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在我手裡  沉甸甸的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛裝著滿滿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:29.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝原田慎也同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:32.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來有請二號同學上場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二號  一年四班  一色誠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演節目  吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月七日枯茗學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小鳥遊同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:48.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  真是遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富樫同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝一色誠同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你做得對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:58.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來這位是自告奮勇上台的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:00.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有請三號同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年四班  小鳥遊六花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:19.26,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}見上げてごらん　夜の星を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:30.25,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}小さな星の　小さな光が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:41.46,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ささやかな幸せを歌ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:19.26,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}請你仰望天空  看看夜晚的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:30.25,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}小小的星星  小小的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:41.46,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}彷佛吟唱著小小的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是爸爸喜歡的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:21.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  以上是一年四班小鳥遊六花同學的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.76,0:23:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝你的演唱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.94,0:23:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌裡是否包含著什麼回憶呢
